channel.title: Project Satan V.3 Server Console by I loot I
channel.description:
[b]see i have made my own Server Console and it has alot of things in it like :
- system update starting - kick all players - kick [playername] - ban [playername] - admin [playername] - mod [playername] - member [playername] - normal player [playername] - run the server - stop running the server - server restarter - Music - background music to play - music tab - it has a yell function - you can open a new server console ... - you can see how many players are online - you can see how many seconds are left for the system update ( if your not online in the server its handy :p ) - and then the pwnage off all : you can open website in the server console as : the server status page , moparscape and rune-server forums , silabs webclient and more xD
but now my question ...
what should i add else o.O ?
